Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

Tra bullismo, shock culturali e divisioni di classe, si innamora di Antara Shukla, una studentessa dell'ultimo anno con aspirazioni politiche e ben oltre la sua portata. Quando una sfida umiliante si scontra con i suoi crescenti sentimenti e una crisi familiare a casa, Rajveer deve lottare pi√π duramente che mai, questa volta non per la gloria, ma per l'amore, la dignit√† e la sopravvivenza.

Informazioni su Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player √® il principale servizio di intrattenimento gratuito, premium e con pubblicit√† in India. Offre una vasta gamma di serie web pluripremiate, reality show, popolari programmi internazionali e un'ampia libreria di film di diversi generi. Con una forte attenzione ai contenuti originali, Amazon MX Player ha lanciato alcuni dei programmi pi√π importanti in India, tra cui Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who's your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter - Totega Nahi Todega e molti altri. Where: JSCA International Stadium Complex, Ranchi

Team News

India

Yashasvi Jaiswal has been patiently waiting for this opportunity to add to his solitary ODI cap. He is expected to open alongside Rohit but India have calls to make in the middle order. Rahul has confirmed that he would bat at six so an allrounder could slot in at five if India seek a sixth option with the ball.

Probable XI: Rohit Sharma, Yashasvi Jaiswal, Virat Kohli, Rishabh Pant (WK), Nitish Reddy, KL Rahul (C), Ravindra Jadeja, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Arshdeep Singh

South Africa

Quinton de Kock's successful comeback to 50-over cricket and Aiden Markram's return should keep Ryan Rickelton out for now. Matthew Breetzke will have to shoulder a lot of responsibility in the middle order after making a spectacular start to his ODI career.

Probable XI: Aiden Markram, Quinton de Kock (WK), Temba Bavuma (C), Matthew Breetzke, Rubin Hermann, Dewald Brevis, Marco Jansen, Corbin Bosch, Keshav Maharaj, Nandre Burger, Lungi Ngidi

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

This musical gem is a journey into the heart of melody and emotion, a song that transcends the boundaries of time and language, leaving an indelible mark on the soul.

Chitra's enchanting vocals in "Kehna Hi Kya" effortlessly convey the depths of love and longing, creating a musical experience that resonates with every listener. With its poetic lyrics and evocative composition, this song has become an anthem of romance and a testament to the power of music to touch the heart.

snippet.title: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Lyrical | Lata Mangeshkar | Suresh Wadkar | Prem Rog | Rishi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Relive the magic of classic Bollywood with the soulful duet ‚ÄúMeri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad‚Äù sung by the legendary Lata Mangeshkar and Suresh Wadkar. Featured in the iconic movie Prem Rog starring Rishi Kapoor, this lyrical video brings out the emotion, romance, and timeless charm of old Hindi melodies. üé∂‚ù§Ô∏è

Don‚Äôt forget to like, share for more musical journeys through Bollywood‚Äôs golden era. üëâ Subscribe to Our channel:  https://youtube.com/@SureshWadkarOldSongs-m5c?si=NbrZmfXqKqNRco1a 

Song Credits:
Song: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad
Artist: Lata Mangeshkar, Suresh Wadkar
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Amir Qazalbash

Film Credits:
Film: Prem Rog
Director: Raj Kapoor
Producer: Randhir Kapoor
Star Cast: Rishi Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, Shammi Kapoor, Nanda, Tanuja, Kulbhushan Kharbanda, Om Prakash, Bindu, Vijayendra, Kiran Vairale, Raza Murad

 Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Song Lyrics 
meree kismat me too nahee shaayad, kyon teraa intjaar karata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo
aaj samajee hoo pyaar ko shaayad, aaj mai tujhako pyaar karatee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

sochata hoo ke meree aankho ne, kyon sajaaye the pyaar ke sapne
tujhase maangee thee ek khushee maine, tune gham bhee nahee diye apane
jindagee bojh ban gayee abb toh, abb toh jita hoo aur naa marata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo

abb naa tute yeh pyaar ke rishte, abb yeh rishte sanbhaalane honge
meree raaho se tujhako kal kee tarah, dukh ke kaante nikaalane honge
mil naa jaye khushee ke raste me, gam kee parchhayeeyo se daratee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

dil nahee ikhtiyaar me mere, jaan jaayegee pyaar me tere
tujhase milane kee aas hain aa jaa, meree duniya uadas hain aa jaa
pyaar shaayad isiko kahate hai, har ghadee bekaraar rahata hoo
raat din teree yaad aatee hai, raat din intjaar karatee hoo

mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo
aaj samajee hoo pyaar ko shaayad, aaj mai tujhako pyaar karatee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

sochata hoo ke meree aankho ne, kyon sajaaye the pyaar ke sapne
tujhase maangee thee ek khushee maine, tune gham bhee nahee diye apane
jindagee bojh ban gayee abb toh, abb toh jita hoo aur naa marata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo

abb naa tute yeh pyaar ke rishte, abb yeh rishte sanbhaalane honge
meree raaho se tujhako kal kee tarah, dukh ke kaante nikaalane honge
mil naa jaye khushee ke raste me, gam kee parchhayeeyo se daratee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

dil nahee ikhtiyaar me mere, jaan jaayegee pyaar me tere
tujhase milane kee aas hain aa jaa, meree duniya uadas hain aa jaa
pyaar shaayad isiko kahate hai, har ghadee bekaraar rahata hoo
raat din teree yaad aatee hai, raat din intjaar karatee hoo
